-- B y   P a t r i c k   M c K i e r n a n
-- 
2011-08-04T12:43:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-04/gold-futures-advance-to-record-1-679-90-an-ounce-on-comex-in-new-york.html
Gold futures for December delivery
rose as much as 0.8 percent to a record $1,679.70 an ounce on
the Comex in  New York .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
